  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a7b14fb3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXk6nChAKBMe7uP708vx06g3hSZBx8L2v0ejP71CqtbDKU7CxnB0ibDMooeOWiaGuyGiaPribQFq8E5DMA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"border:1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);border-radius:12px;padding:0px 0px;margin:0px 0px;font-weight:400;font-family:PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"border:1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);border-radius:12px;padding:0px 0px;margin:0px 0px;color:inherit;font-weight:400;font-family:PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <h2>\n     <p style=\"margin:0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:1em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: inherit;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">我发现！</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:1.8;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: inherit;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">我们现在教AI看世界的方式，可能存在缺陷。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:1.8;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: inherit;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">特别是视频理解，</span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-weight: 400;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin: 0px 0px;padding: 0px 0px;border: 1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 12px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin: 0px 0px;padding: 0px 0px;border: 1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 12px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #1B1B1B;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;margin: 16px 0;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">目前大多数多模态模型，用的都是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">每秒一帧</span>的抽帧方式来理解视频。说白了就是一张张静止的照片，没有过渡没有前因后果。</span></span></p>\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n     <div style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:1.8;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI只能靠猜，</span></p>\n      <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"border:1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);border-radius:12px;padding:0px 0px;margin:0px 0px;color:inherit;font-weight:400;font-family:PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"4 4 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-weight: 400;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin: 0px 0px;padding: 0px 0px;border: 1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 12px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">\n       <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">它能看到A，看到B，却看不到从A到B的那个至关重要的过渡箭头。</span></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">但昨天，</span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-weight: bold;color: #000000 !important;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">面壁智能</span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">发布了他们小钢炮系列的最新型号，</span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-weight: bold;color: #000000 !important;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">MiniCPM-V 4.5</span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:1em;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">🔗&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">github.com/OpenBMB/MiniCPM-o</span></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">🔗 huggingface.co/openbmb/MiniCPM-V-4_5</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">🔗 modelscope.cn/models/OpenBMB/MiniCPM-V-4_5</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">在一堆SOTA成绩和技术名词里，我看到了一个词，</span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-weight: bold;color: #000000 !important;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">高刷视频理解</span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一反应就是，这真的有用吗？平时我看30帧和60帧的视频也没太大感觉，但是如果把这个范围从1秒1帧，提升到1秒20帧，20倍的增幅就很有看头了。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">看看这些案例。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">先<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">给&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-weight: bold;color: #000000 !important;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">MiniCPM-V 4.5 一段</span></span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">行车记录仪的视频，让它</span></span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-weight: bold;color: #000000 !important;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">记录下沿途所有出现过的店铺名称。</span></span></span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以看到，画面随着车辆的行驶快速移动，街道两旁的店铺、广告牌、路标一闪而过，如果是过去每秒一帧的模型，面对这种充满动态模糊、视角不断变化的场景，是大量的错漏和无法识别。而 MiniCPM-V 4.5 准确识别出了那些高速掠过的招牌，甚至连一些角度刁钻的小字都捕捉到了。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二个 case 是速算挑战，前段时间我还去炸鱼小学生，简单来说屏幕上会不停刷新数字、公式和符号，构成一道数学题。我们需要在炒鸡短的时间内看清题目并给出答案。</span></span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">Amazing啊，这个场景剥离了现实元素，变成对模型视觉处理速度的极限施压。MiniCPM-V 4.5 能捕捉到闪现的数字们，按照正确的顺序，组成算式，最终得出答案。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果说前两个展示了模型在动态环境下的信息捕捉能力，那么第三个case，指向了更高维度的理解力。可以理解这段视频是快闪广告，汉堡、薯条、派、可乐等商品图片以极快的速度轮播出现。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">问题是，可乐是在第几个出现的？</span></span></span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个低抽帧的模型，能告诉我视频里出现了可乐，但由于它丢失了中间的关键帧，看到的是一堆散落的素材，会搞错商品的出现顺序。高帧的MiniCPM-V 4.5看到的是一条由视觉元素构成的、有先后顺序的时间线，所以它能判断可乐出现的顺序。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次的MiniCPM-V 4.5，仅仅用了8B的参数量，就在OpenCompass上，超越了GPT-4o、Gemini-2.0-Pro 和 72B的Qwen2.5-VL。</span></span></p>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 18px;display: flex;justify-content: space-between;flex-shrink: 0;\">\n     <div key=\"24\" style=\"display: inline-block;flex: 1;color: inherit;font-size: 16px;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;line-height: 2em;margin: 0;minHeight: 20px;letterSpacing: auto;padding: 0 4px;\">\n      <div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n        <p style=\"display: inline-block;margin: 0px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;border-radius: 5px;line-height: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015839\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3574074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=963c3192&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYEhakvKZjXk6nChAKBMe7uP708vx06g3jiaFYThBP88IU03TwbgbqQDKKmh6SMxaxPZeKicQxgUgMhvgz6WjuQMA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div key=\"26\" style=\"display: inline-block;flex: 1;color: inherit;font-size: 16px;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;line-height: 2em;margin: 0;minHeight: 20px;letterSpacing: auto;padding: 0 4px;\">\n      <div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n        <p style=\"display: inline-block;margin: 0px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;border-radius: 5px;line-height: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015836\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3333333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=287eec19&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYEhakvKZjXk6nChAKBMe7uP708vx06g3XS38yazB9roP7YbkrxGSJ3jCsa9zmqQiayRXORCf7a2KKLP4lAERCRg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">除了赋予它动态视觉的3D-Resampler，它还用了一种很聪明的方式来学习处理文档。在一份文档里，对文字区域随机施加不同程度的噪点。当噪点很轻时，模型就学习OCR，努力识别这些文字。当噪点很重，文字完全无法辨认时，模型就进入知识学习模式，它必须根据图片的上下文，去推理和还原这些文字的含义。</span></span></p>\n    <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n     <p style=\"display: inline-block;margin: 0px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;border-radius: 5px;line-height: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015837\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3333333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0218f3b9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYEhakvKZjXk6nChAKBMe7uP708vx06g3JYcaQGgNVXZvbptdSxuH5TUibTG12O2GiajTjeKV6PGmLAoFbOFsuE4Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:1.8;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">在 OmniDocBench 榜单上，MiniCPM-V 4.5的 OverallEdit、TextEdit、TableEdit 三项指标取得了通用多模态模型同级别的 SOTA 表现。</span></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个方法把识别文字和理解知识这两件原本割裂的事情，统一了起来。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">MiniCPM-V 4.5还有一个优势，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">它是一个8B的端侧模型</span>，在视频理解任务中，处理时间的开销，只有同级别模型的十分之一。</span></span></p>\n    <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n     <p style=\"display: inline-block;margin: 0px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;border-radius: 5px;line-height: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015838\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3574074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4ee72769&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYEhakvKZjXk6nChAKBMe7uP708vx06g3qwSwBPfZbOU5pZciaZBMnNCcom6ORd3VvmJbB2WbylNKicVOo3Seeb3g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我都能想象到，搭载</span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-weight: 400;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin: 0px 0px;padding: 0px 0px;border: 1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 12px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin: 0px 0px;padding: 0px 0px;border: 1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 12px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #1B1B1B;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;margin: 16px 0;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">MiniCPM-V 4.5的</span></span><span leaf=\"\">AR眼镜可以实时分析对面谈判者的微表情，在你耳边轻声提示你，对方在听到某个条款时，眼神和嘴角发生了什么细微的情绪变化。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">或者是一个智能灶具，可以看着你切菜的视频，实时告诉你，你的刀法在哪个瞬间出现了偏差，应该如何调整。再或者是一个运动App，可以通过手机摄像头，捕捉你深蹲时身体姿态变化告诉你发力点是否正确。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015867\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"2.0657407407407407\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=792f1c43&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXk6nChAKBMe7uP708vx06g3NywryWoznFQgtH3sJpZtY1RB9A2nwQmk3uFexCMAGFBblA8zEZaFbg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">从这个角度看，面壁智能在多模态领域，似乎走出了一条非常独特的路。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">他们选择去啃如何让模型真正理解动态的世界，如何让强大的能力以一种极其高效、低耗的方式，运行在我们手边的每一个设备。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">高刷视频理解</span>，这个听起来有些极客的词，</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">它让AI有机会去理解那些稍纵即逝的过程，</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">去捕捉那些转瞬即逝的意图。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">世界是流动的，每分每秒都有新的故事在发生，</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">一个一秒只能看到几帧画面的AI，永远无法真正理解我们的世界</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在，</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">那扇通往流动世界的大门，</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">被面壁推开了一条缝。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">@ 作者 / 卡尔&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "面壁智能 MiniCPM-V 4.5 模型通过高刷视频理解和高效端侧推理，在多模态领域实现突破，超越主流模型。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "面壁智能 MiniCPM-V 4.5 模型通过高刷视频理解和高效端侧推理，在多模态领域实现突破，超越主流模型。",
  "summary": "文章深入介绍了面壁智能最新发布的 MiniCPM-V 4.5 多模态模型，其核心创新在于显著提升了视频理解的帧率，从传统每秒一帧提升至每秒 20 帧，有效解决了现有模型在处理动态视频时因信息丢失而导致的理解局限性。文章通过行车记录仪店铺识别、速算挑战和快闪广告顺序判断等生动案例，展示了 MiniCPM-V 4.5 在复杂动态场景下卓越的信息捕捉和高维度理解能力。技术层面，该模型采用了 3D-Resampler 实现动态视觉，并创新性地通过随机噪声学习方法统一了文字识别与知识理解。尽管参数量仅为 8B，MiniCPM-V 4.5 在 OpenCompass 和 OmniDocBench 等基准测试中表现出色，超越了包括 GPT-4o 在内的多款主流大模型，同时作为端侧模型，其视频处理时间开销仅为同级别模型的十分之一。文章最后展望了 MiniCPM-V 4.5 在 AR 眼镜、智能灶具、运动 App 等领域的广泛应用前景，强调了面壁智能在推动 AI 真正理解动态世界并实现高效边缘部署方面的独特路径。",
  "mainPoints": [
